content: yungalgo: Merged 5 PRs this month, with significant contributions to plugin functionality and CLI improvements, notably PR #4031 which added over 21k lines for enhanced plugin installation and GitHub authentication UX. Fixed various issues across the codebase, including plugin publishing (PR #4095, +5755/-1488 lines) and core swarm component linting (PR #3761, +1086/-984 lines). Demonstrated occasional activity throughout the month, focusing primarily on bugfixes (48%) with substantial code changes across 44 files.
